title: About
text:
Hi! My name is Kevin Ong and this is my personal blog. I’m also known as lobakbro through the interwebs!
I am a machine learning engineer that lives in 🌉 San Francisco, California. My professional interests are in deep learning!
My other interests include classical music ♫♬ (Rachmaninoff, Sibelius, and Mahler), plants 🌱, a perfect 🍜 bowl of beef noodle soup (bun bo & lanzhou la mian)
This blog is built with <3 with Quarto.
